{"tid":147574,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"我隻貓咁樣係咪唔正常？","createTime":"2017-03-08T02:59:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-10T08:47:02.000Z","uid":88272,"like":29,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b9646dace7cdf47e06dad3d846e077a1f2791eb2","tid":147574,"uid":88272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T02:59:30.000Z","msg":"每朝起身嘅時候，我隻貓都會行去我腳邊，反轉個身露個肚俾我睇，但係我一摸佢個肚，佢又會抓我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UxL8TxD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUxL8TxD.jpg&h=e7726501&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n影唔到佢抓我嘅時候<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f350e4242532b4b62f1e2f421d13a05943c73ec3","tid":147574,"uid":32749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T03:01:13.000Z","msg":"俾你睇但冇過俾你摸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be89a5a36a9df64aff5e103a073340641f0a75ad","tid":147574,"uid":32749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T03:01:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>俾你睇但冇話俾你摸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e03978185208b62d6f24847fc203a3dc2a3a8d5","tid":147574,"uid":89608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T03:02:51.000Z","msg":"佢係咪想表達俾你知佢有病, 唔係叫你摸佢"},{"pid":"8a26a6ada7a466f4745f286be0e184edd44e5748","tid":147574,"uid":88272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T03:06:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢係咪想表達俾你知佢有病, 唔係叫你摸佢</blockquote><br />\n例如<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  肚痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"157e693eb0b2b6d9bdc