\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔好摸咁多同埋咁耐 萬一隻貓真係憎咗人摸肚就真係無嫁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbbb176e733b8efd6f45885a535a2faaa1cdc818","tid":147574,"uid":57835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T05:10:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>根本貓公貓乸都係臭閪港女黎<br />\n未夠100歲都唔好俾飽飯佢地食</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a7710235b696c5c4df468937ac82aff52094cd3","tid":147574,"uid":70361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T05:10:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"https://youtu.be/KEbtXkd2XF4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FKEbtXkd2XF4&d=LSsgDEuqvL%2F6lC7PehFbgwHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=60d2cbbf\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/KEbtXkd2XF4</a><br />\n<br />\n呢度有講點解<br />\n睇多啲佢啲片 好有用</blockquote><br />\n幾正喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42fc6532d1c22bda9be541cb655f2010e502fb8f","tid":147574,"uid":1895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T05:22:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/j86cs11.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fj86cs11.jpg&h=095f051c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢隻都係成日咬鳩我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c4f4665d827cc64098c33ce2596c91d8f21e864","tid":147574,"uid":54929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T05:33:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36a2610db316411373cecbd439b5f27f62b3b12d","tid":147574,"uid":80734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T05:34:18.000Z","msg":"我有一隻都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/08/133007_b51fe284974d966a136c2a5c715abae0.jp